a_{n}-a_{n+1}=(2n+1)\left(\dfrac{1}{n^2(n+1)^2}+\cdots+\dfrac{1}{(n^2+2n)(n^2+4n+1)}\right)-\dfrac{1}{n^2+4n+2}-\dfrac{1}{n^2+4n+3}
a_{n}-a_{n+1}>\dfrac{(2n+1)^2}{(n^2+2n)(n^2+4n+1)}-\dfrac{2}{n^2+4n+1}=\dfrac{2n^2+1}{(n^2+2n)(n^2+4n+1)}>0
